OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Executive has
OL,7,Freversed plans to overhaul children's
OL,8,Fsocial care, abandoning its commitment
OL,9,Fto establish a new regional body
OL,10,Fdespite repeated warnings that
OL,11,Fchildren and families are being let
OL,12,Fdown.
OL,14,FThe decision marks a significant U-
OL,15,Fturn on one of the key recommendations
OL,16,Ffrom the Independent Review of
OL,17,FChildren's Social Care Services,
OL,18,Fpublished in 2023 which called for 53
OL,19,Freforms to transform support for
OL,20,Fchildren and families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAt the heart of the review was the
OL,7,Fcreation of a new Children and
OL,8,FFamilies Regional Authority, designed
OL,9,Fto give children's social care greater
OL,10,Ffocus, improve accountability and
OL,11,Fdrive reform across government.
OL,13,FJust three months ago, Professor Ray
OL,14,FJones, who led the independent review,
OL,15,Fwas told the Executive intended to
OL,16,Fmove forward with the recommendation.
OL,18,FBut last week, ministers confirmed
OL,19,Fthose plans would no longer proceed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FProfessor Jones told UTV he remains
OL,7,F"anxious, angry, despondent and
OL,8,Fdismayed", warning that Northern
OL,9,FIreland continues to shy away from
OL,10,Fmaking the difficult decisions needed
OL,11,Fto deliver lasting change.
OL,13,FHe argues that a child's future can be
OL,14,Fshaped by the support available around
OL,15,Fthem, and for many vulnerable young
OL,16,Fpeople that support comes from the
OL,17,Fcare system and social services.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe Executive said it had explored
OL,7,Fcreating a new Regional Authority for
OL,8,Fchildren's social care but concluded
OL,9,Fthat "now is not the right time"
OL,10,Fbecause of the scale of the work
OL,11,Finvolved, the costs and the wider
OL,12,Fchanges required across the system.
OL,14,FInstead, ministers insist reform will
OL,15,Fcontinue through existing structures.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
