PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FOne parent, whose identity we are
OL,7,Fprotecting because of their experience
OL,8,Fof the care system, described the
OL,9,Fchallenges families continue to face
OL,10,Fand questioned whether enough is being
OL,11,Fdone to improve outcomes for children.
OL,13,FThe latest figures underline the scale
OL,14,Fof the pressures facing the system.
OL,16,FMore than 4,000 children and young
OL,17,Fpeople are now being looked after in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland that's the highest
OL,19,Fnumber recorded in almost three
OL,20,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised that without
OL,7,Freform vulnerable children will
OL,8,Fcontinue to miss out on the support
OL,9,Fthey need.
OL,11,FOrganisations working with children
OL,12,Fand families say attention must now
OL,13,Fturn to what happens next and whether
OL,14,Fministers can deliver meaningful
OL,15,Fimprovements without implementing the
OL,16,Freview's central recommendation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FIn a statement, The Executive Office
OL,7,Fsaid ministers had carefully
OL,8,Fconsidered establishing a new Children
OL,9,Fand Families Regional Authority but
OL,10,Fconcluded the proposal would require
OL,11,Fprimary legislation, take at least
OL,12,Ffour years to deliver and cost a
OL,13,Fminimum of #4.68 million.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783774108
OL,3,CExecutive U-turn on children's care
OL,4,Creform in Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"While the Executive supported
OL,7,Fexploring possible steps to reform
OL,8,Fchildren's social care, with a view to
OL,9,Festablishing a new Regional Authority,
OL,10,Fthe work undertaken by the Ministers
OL,11,Fof Health and Justice has concluded
OL,12,Fthat now is not the right time to
OL,13,Fprogress such an arm's-length body.
OL,15,F"This reflects the scale of the
OL,16,Fexercise in terms of time, cost and
OL,17,Fwider changes needed across the system
OL,18,Falongside the changed landscape since
OL,19,Fthe proposal was first considered."
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
